    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains factory-rigid with preventative subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is managed via the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. Every bushing, seal, and mechanical tolerance meets or exceeds OEM specifications. This is a collector-grade example with flawless compression and a fully documented service history.",
